        <abstract> 
<p>Informs CD third edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> is exhausted. Proposes a new edition. Has CD any changes? Since demand is slowing up, proposes printing only 1250 copies and deferring payment of CD’s share until sales have repaid manufacturing costs.</p> 
